<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠٣ - <span class="c2">(١٨٧٦)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَاهُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3889">أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5820">وَأَبُو كُرَيْبٍ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5879">ابْنُ فُضَيْلٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4642">عُمَارَةَ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>